name: NSValueTransformerName
desc: Named value transformers defined by NSValueTransformer.

items.name: static let isNilTransformerName: NSValueTransformerName
items.desc: This value transformer returns true if the value is nil.

items.name: static let isNotNilTransformerName: NSValueTransformerName
items.desc: This value transformer returns true if the value is non-nil.

items.name: static let negateBooleanTransformerName: NSValueTransformerName
items.desc: This value transformer negates a boolean value, transforming true to false and false to true.

items.name: static let secureUnarchiveFromDataTransformerName: NSValueTransformerName
items.desc: The name of the value transformer that creates then returns an object by attempting to unarchive the data to a class that supports secure coding.
